Biography

2021-22

- Finished 10th in the 200-back at the MAAC Championships with a season-best time of 1:51.22.

- Finished 13th in the 50-free at the MAAC Championships with a personal-best time of 20.93.

- Finished 14th in the 100-back at the MAAC Championships with a personal-best time of 51.51.

- Swam a personal-best 1:45.25 in the 200-free at the Bucknell Invitational.

- Member of the MAAC All-Academic team.

2020-21

- Member of the 2020-21 swimming & diving team.

- Member of the MAAC All-Academic team.

2019-20

- ECAC qualifier in the 50-free.

- ECAC qualifier in the 100-free.

- ECAC qualifier in the 100-back.

- Finished eighth in the 200-back at the MAAC Championships with a season-best time of 1:50.28.

- Finished 13th in the 200-IM at the MAAC Championships with a personal-best time of 1:52.65.

- Finished 14th in the 200-free at the MAAC Championships with a personal-best time of 1:41.77.

- Swam a personal-best 21.18 in the 50-free at the ECAC Championships.

- Swam a personal-best 46.12 in the 100-free at the ECAC Championships.

- Swam a personal-best 51.58 in the 100-back at the ECAC Championships.

- Member of the MAAC All-Academic team.

2018-19

- Came in 14th in the 200 IM with a time of 1:53.61 at the MAAC Championships.

- Finished in 10th-place in the 200 back at the MAAC Championships with a time of 1:49.72.

- Ended up in 13th-place in the 100 back with a time of 52.41 at the ECAC Championships.

- Won the 100 back at a pair of dual meets during the year.

BEFORE RIDER

Was a member of the varsity swimming team at the Good Hope Country Day School.

PERSONAL

Son of Whitney Young…from the United States Virgin Islands…majoring in business.
